cyCastleObjectInputStream(ByteArrayInputStream input) throws Exception {\n        super(input);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    protected Class<?> resolveClass(ObjectStreamClass description) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException {\n        if (BCDSTU4145PrivateKey.class.getName().equals(description.getName())) {\n            return BCDSTU4145PrivateKey.class;\n        }\n        return super.resolveClass(description);\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThis addresses the Native Image deserialization failure where `ObjectInputStream` could not resolve:\n\n```text\norg.bouncycastle.jcajce.provider.asymmetric.dstu.BCDSTU4145PrivateKey\n```\n\nThe test still focuses only on `BCDSTU4145PrivateKey` and continues to exercise:\n\n- `BCDSTU4145PrivateKey.writeObject`\n- `BCDSTU4145PrivateKey.readObject`\n- the nested calls to:\n  - `ObjectOutputStream.writeObject(...)`\n  - `ObjectInputStream.readObject()`\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a5ca05b55ea51830169fbd4dded5c8192831a16c10eecb8f5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1276, "output": 1216, "cacheRead": 52736, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 55228, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778111695642, "responseId": "resp_0a5ca05b55ea51830169fbd4d0bb448192a3c7754ae84b8958"}}
